## Verification Plan

### Browser Testing
1. Start backend: `cd c:\Users\Public\Linguability\backend && npm run dev`
2. Start frontend: `cd c:\Users\Public\Linguability\frontend && npm run dev`
3. Navigate to `/practice` → verify "Writing" appears as 4th practice type
4. Select a language → click Writing → verify canvas loads with a prompt
5. Draw on canvas → verify drawing works (mouse/touch)
6. Toggle to type mode → type a response → submit
7. Verify NLP feedback appears with score and detailed breakdown
8. Test with intentional misspelling → verify partial credit

### Manual API Test
```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3001/api/evaluate/written \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"language":"hindi","promptId":1,"userResponse":"namaste"}'
```
Verify the response includes `overallScore`, `feedback`, and `acceptedAlternatives`.
